SaharaReporters Media The Federal Capital Territory Police Command has confirmed the killing of an innocent Nigerian by its personnel on Tuesday during a protest by members of the Islamic Movement in Nigeria. A statement by spokesperson for the police in the command, DSP Anjuguri Manzah, confirmed the report by SaharaReporters. The statement reads, “The FCT Police Command has successful restored calm around Berger round-about after a protest by members of Islamic Movement in Nigeria. 



